<title>Isa Táńirim, barlyq ómirim</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Eı, Isa Táńirim, barlyq ómirim
 Tek Ózińmen maılanǵanyn men kórdim
 // Ózińnen basqa, Táńir joq asqan,
 Júrekke sózin Rýhymen basqan e-e-ı!
 Qudaıym - Sen! Júrek Iesi! //

[C1]
   // Baq qonyp basqa, tynym kelip janǵa,
   Ózińmen Isa,
   Ózińnen artyq,
   Júrekke ystyq, eshkim joq basqa.
   Jamandyq ketip, jaqsylyq egip,
   Sen janymyzǵa, aq bata berip
   Jarylqaý tógip, aldyń qushaǵyńa. //
   Eı, jan tynyshtyǵyn,</lyrics>
</song>